extendedInfo.description: The physicians at Sabates Eye Centers are health care professionals who have been dedicated to providing comprehensive high quality eye care services for over 45 years. We have twelve facilities, including office center eye clinics and university locations conveniently located in the greater Kansas City area so you can easily access the very best in eye care.Our physicians are specialty trained doctors, educators and researchers specializing in advanced retinal treatment and surgery, diabetic retinopathy, glaucoma, advanced cataract procedures, surgery and lens replacement, macular degeneration, ophthalmic plastic and reconstructive procedures, pediatric ophthalmology, corneal diseases and surgery, neuro-ophthalmology, ocular oncology, advanced refractive procedures, comprehensive eye care and more.We have this distinguished and diverse group of physicians in so many different areas for one reason only: to have a qualified specialist immediately accessible for our patients and referring physicians.And that's the way it should be.TM
